   &UR; CULTURE (Moved in ``e'' category) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   NYC-SEX (New York) _ New York City may be the most diversified,
competitive, high-priced flesh market in the world, especially in
summer. On certain evenings as the streets teem with gym-toned
bodies and attitudes to match you have the sense of a million
sexual fantasies in the naked city converging in one giant
imaginary orgy. Paradoxically, two recent films and an HBO series
suggest that these fantasies may be as isolated from one another as
the thoughts of solitary exiles dreaming away their nights on
lonely desert islands. A critic's notebook by Stephen Holden.
