<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-20 02:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6597 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBO-ANGELS-REWRITE-LA     07-20 0460
