</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Large and small investors need asset allocation
 &HT;    By Hank Ezell
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Asset allocation is a core concept for investors, from
the richest ones down to the rest of us.
