<DOCNO> NYT19990720.0094 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-20 12:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6911 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC &LR; - &UR; FONDA-BRIDGET-LADN     07-20 0955
