New York City but are finding only booked hotels and inflated
prices, you might consider an apartment in a Manhattan neighborhood
for Christmas through New Year's. Prices range from $99 to $275 a
night. For details, call A Hospitality Company at 800-987-125 or
visit www.hospitalitycompany.com.
</P>
