laid-back beauty flourishes alongside rugged canyons (Includes
4-column color photo of Anini Beach, one 18-pica color photo of
Lumahai Beach and one 18-pica color illustration for headline
treatment.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: ESSENTIALS OF KAUAI: Tips for traveling in Kauai.
(Includes a 2-column color map illustration of the island of
Kauai.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: IN PRINT: Travel writer Bill Bryson takes a long, strange
trip back to his home country. (Includes 1-column color photo of
book.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRAVEL BRIEFS: Denmark has proclaimed 1999 its Medieval
Year, highlighting the many archeological digs, burial mounds,
churches and museums of that nation.
</P>
