<HEADLINE>
SUMMER ACCENT ON HERBS 
</HEADLINE>
   (ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.)  
 (af)  
 This is the first of eight columns by Waldy Malouf, the chef and an
owner of Beacon in Manhattan. His collaborator on these columns is
Melissa Clark.  
 By WALDY MALOUF   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   If fresh fruits and vegetables are the vocabulary of summer,
