<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    HIRING OF AIDE HIGHLIGHTS GORE'S TANGLED HISTORY ON TOBACCO
ISSUE
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) politics categories.
 &HT;    By SCOTT SHEPARD
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
