   CYC-TOUR (Piau-Engaly, France) _ Spaniard Fernardo Escartin
pedals past thousands of cheering fans to not just win the race,
but to shake up the standings. By Susan Bickelhaupt. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-MARLINS-REDSOX (Boston) _ By Gordon Edes.
