<P>
   APPLE-FUTURE (New York) _ Steve Jobs has saved Apple Computer
from oblivion. Now what? Jobs to give MacWorld keynote address
Wednesday. By Hiawatha Bray. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   ENGAGE-IPO (Undated) _ Engage Technologies becomes the latest
child of CMGI to go public, more than doubling in price in the
first day of trading. By Diane E. Lewis. 600 words.
</P>
