   TRAVEL-BRIEFS (Undated) _ Disney's second ship: Ahoy, Little
Mermaid; Edinburgh landmark opens as festival site; Two Manatees
star in Cincinnati exhibit; Now skiers can stay at a summer
behemoth; Toys in the pre-Nintendo era. (Moved).
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-Q&AMP;A (Undated) _ Travel questions and answers: Ticks on
Nantucket; Victory ships; Tickets for the Derby. By Paul Freireich.
(Moved).
</P>
<P>
   PRACTICAL-TRAVELER (Undated) _ A new spot in Florida tries to
bring eco-tourism into the mainstream. By Betsy Wade. (Moved).
</P>
