and held her hands up against them. The hands are very white
indeed. `Oh, great,' she said. `I don't know what's wrong with me
now. They do look pale. Sometimes they turn gray, too. I don't
know. I asked the doctor, and he's like, ``Weird!'' ' ''
</P>
