<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-20 20:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7581 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TRADE-REPORT-ART-NYT &LR;      07-20 0530
