computer study of the payrolls of all 30 major league teams shows
both the Dodgers and Orioles are spending more than $1 million per
victory _ highest in the majors _ yet both clubs are languishing in
the depths of the standings. 
By Frank Giradot/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
